title: Netherlands 2 Year Note Yield
description: Netherlands 2Y Bond Yield was 2.12 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Netherlands 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 4.92 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Netherlands 2Y Bond Yield.
